#itskaytobeyou ❤️💃

Just before the lockdown I had planned a trip to my moms school in Madurai , I remember being so sick and wanting to cancel but it was the annual day at school and all the kids were performing. 
So I went , and from the minute I reached to when I left ,all we did was laugh . The joy with which the kids danced and performed was incredible. Including a part of Snow White and seven dwarfs skit, where there was a giraffe appearance ( which they explained me was because they could not find a horse costume in Madurai , the show must go on , always make the best of every situation 🙂) .
All the teachers were so warm and caring , to see the kids in such a wonderful environment it was just so heartening. One of the sayings by a great soul “if you want to find peace , help others “. @reliefprojectsindia #mountainviewschoolindia 🏫

In all the moments when I have faced struggles, it has always been the stories of inspiring women who have motivated me to keep going - I’m so excited to share with you what we have been working on at Kay beauty - presenting KAY KONVERSATIONS- where we are featuring women who have overcome obstacles and faced their fears to realize their dreams . 
-we don’t fit into moulds 
-we are all unique and special 
Beauty is about celebrating that uniqueness and being authentic to who you are - after all #itskaytobeyou

Our first Kay Konversation features Ayesha Billimoria. An athlete whose journey to the Olympics was interrupted by an accident. But that did not stop her from bouncing back and inspiring millions of others.

"Every setback is a setup for success, because when you fail you learn something. Don’t give up in the pursuit of your goals" - Ayesha Billimoria 💪🏼@fitgirl.india

@kaybykatrina #KayBeauty #KayByKatrina #ItsKayToBeYou #KayKonversations

This journey is not only ours but also all the women who have embraced themselves the way they truly are. ❤️💁🏻‍♀️Stay tuned as we have a lot of interesting launches lined up....... coming 🔜 💋

#KayBeauty #KayByKatrina #KayBeautyTurns1 #NykaaxKayBeauty #MakeupThatKares
